# Portfolio Website (aryancodes.tech)

## Stack

- React 18 + Vite 5 + Tailwind 3 + React Router 6
- Deployed on Vercel ([vercel.json](vercel.json))
- Analytics: lazy-loaded `@vercel/analytics`

## Design language (do not change without explicit request)

- **Colors:** HSL CSS variables in [src/index.css](src/index.css) - `--ink`, `--paper`, `--surface`, `--signal`, `--signal-deep`, `--muted`, etc. Use `hsl(var(--token))` in Tailwind arbitrary values.
- **Typography:** Body = Gilroy; headings (`font-display`) = Syne; labels/mono = IBM Plex Mono. Fonts are **self-hosted only** - see [src/styles/fonts.css](src/styles/fonts.css). Never add Google Fonts CDN.
- **Layout:** `content` and `site-shell` wrappers; sections use `surface-card`, `border-2`, offset shadows (`shadow-[6px_6px_0_...]`).
- **Copy & placement:** Do not change visible text, section order, or spacing unless the user asks.

## Constants-first

- URLs, SEO, contact, social links → [src/constants/seo.js](src/constants/seo.js) and [src/constants/urls.js](src/constants/urls.js)
- Public asset paths → [src/constants/assets.js](src/constants/assets.js)
- Section content (experience, education, projects, etc.) → [src/constants/data/](src/constants/data/)
- Empty string checks: use `.length > 0` or `.length === 0`, not truthy checks on strings alone
- Document exported constants and functions with JSDoc `@type` / `@param`

## Images

- Hero and logos: paths from `assets.js`; run `npm run optimize:images` (needs `cwebp`) after changing source images
- Prefer WebP + `srcSet` + explicit `width`/`height` + `loading="lazy"` (except LCP hero: `fetchpriority="high"`)
- Project images live under `public/project_images/` and `public/project_logos/`

## SEO / LCP pipeline

1. Edit [src/constants/seo.js](src/constants/seo.js) (single source of truth for meta, JSON-LD, hero LCP copy).
2. Run `npm run sync:seo` or `npm run build` (`prebuild` runs sync automatically).
3. **Never** hand-edit injected blocks between `<!-- SEO:AUTO_* -->` and `<!-- LCP_* -->` markers in [index.html](index.html).
4. Static LCP shell is generated by [scripts/lcp-shell.mjs](scripts/lcp-shell.mjs).

## Performance (Lighthouse / PageSpeed)

- Keep [Navbar](src/components/Navbar.jsx) + [HeroSection](src/components/HeroSection.jsx) eager; below-fold sections lazy in [Home.jsx](src/pages/Home.jsx) with `Suspense`
- Preserve `manualChunks` in [vite.config.js](vite.config.js); avoid heavy new dependencies (no unused Radix/shadcn - `components.json` is legacy)
- Framer Motion: reuse presets from [src/motion/variants.js](src/motion/variants.js)
- Do not add animation libraries to above-the-fold critical path

## Component patterns

- Section titles: [SectionHeading.jsx](src/components/SectionHeading.jsx) - only pass `kicker` when it should render
- External “Visit” links: [ExternalLinkRow.jsx](src/components/ExternalLinkRow.jsx)
- Clipboard: [useCopyToClipboard.js](src/hooks/useCopyToClipboard.js)
- Résumé URL: `${SITE_URL}${RESUME_PATH}`; Drive redirect: `RESUME_DRIVE_URL` in urls.js

## Accessibility

- Keep `aria-label` on icon-only links, `rel="noopener noreferrer"` on external links, semantic `<main>` / `<section>` / headings
- Hash nav links must remain crawlable (`href="#section"`)

## What not to add

- shadcn/Radix UI unless explicitly requested (bundle size)
- TypeScript migration unless requested
- Google Fonts or third-party font CDNs
